query:
INSERT INTO interaction (
            interaction_type,
            interaction_date,
            subject,
            summary,
            medium,
            application_id,
            person_id,
            company_id
        )
        VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
        RETURNING
            id AS "id!: i64",
            interaction_type AS "interaction_type: InteractionType",
            interaction_date AS "interaction_date!: NaiveDate",
            subject,
            summary,
            medium,
            application_id,
            person_id,
            company_id,
            created_at AS "created_at!: NaiveDateTime",
            updated_at AS "updated_at!: NaiveDateTime"
